text: Huai Ket railway station is a railway station located in Ngiu Rai Subdistrict, Taphan Hin District, Phichit. It is located 324.915 km from Bangkok railway station and is a class 3 railway station. It is on the Northern Line of the State Railway of Thailand. ==Train services== * Ordinary 201/202 Bangkok- Phitsanulok-Bangkok * Local 401/402 Lop Buri-Phitsanulok-Lop Buri * Local 407/408 Nakhon Sawan-Chiang Mai-Nakhon Sawan == References == * * Category:Railway stations in Thailand
